'''天主教烏魯阿蘇教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Uruassuensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Uruaçu}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一個[[天主教|天主教]][[教區|教區]]，包括中部[[戈亞斯州|戈亞斯州]]北部共十九市。教區屬[[天主教巴西利亞總教區|巴西利亞總教區]]。

教區於1956年3月26日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XXIV |year=1957 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=188-190 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-49-1957-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-06-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617165349/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-49-1957-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-06-17 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2010年時有319,000名教友，佔轄區總人口84.8%。教區有27個[[堂區|堂區]]和52位[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-pt|若望·嘉祿·卡爾達斯-巴羅卡|Giovani Carlos Caldas Barroca}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 17.06.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/17/200617a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617160010/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/17/200617a.html |archivedate=2020-06-17 |language=en |date=2020-06-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-pt|若瑟·達-西爾瓦-沙韋斯|José da Silva Chaves}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 03.01.2007 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/01/03/0005/00014.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-06-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617162808/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/01/03/0005/00014.html |archivedate=2020-06-17 |language=it |date=2007-01-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

